@startuml
title Division by Zero Test Execution

actor TestFunction
participant Calculator
boundary PythonRuntime
control "pytest.raises" as PytestRaises

TestFunction -> Calculator : create instance
activate Calculator

TestFunction -> PytestRaises : enter context (expects ZeroDivisionError)
activate PytestRaises

PytestRaises -> Calculator : divide(5, 0)
Calculator -> PythonRuntime : invoke 5 / 0
activate PythonRuntime

PythonRuntime --> Calculator : raise ZeroDivisionError("division by zero")
deactivate PythonRuntime

Calculator --> PytestRaises : ZeroDivisionError propagates
deactivate Calculator

PytestRaises --> TestFunction : exception caught and verified
deactivate PytestRaises

note over TestFunction : test passes — assertion satisfied

@enduml
